Atomic Basin-Integrated Ehrenfest Forces and Basin and Surface Electronic Virial Energies:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  EhF(A) = Electronic Ehrenfest Force on Basin of Atom A, Calculated as Minus Basin
           Integral of Divergence of Stress Tensor
  Vb(A) = Basin Electronic Virial Energy of Atom A = -<r * DivStress>(A)
  Vs(A) = Surface Electronic Virial Energy of Atom A = V(A) - Vb(A)
  V(A) = Total Electronic Virial Energy of Atom A = -K(A) - G(A) = -2T(A)
